  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
          Renovation Done? Let's Finish the Job Right.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Professional post-construction cleaning that actually removes the dust — not just moves it around. Veteran-owned, fully insured, HEPA-equipped.
